  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned",
    "Add the curry powder and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the beef stock concentrate, coconut milk, orange juice, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 20 minutes",
    "Stir in the grated tempering chocolate until melted",
    "Serve hot over rice or with roti"
